{"parse":{"title":"Rindos affair","pageid":27014368,"revid":785530717,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>\n\nThe <b>Rindos affair</b> was an <a href=\"/wiki/Academic_dishonesty\" title=\"Academic dishonesty\">academic scandal</a> that occurred at the <a href=\"/wiki/University_of_Western_Australia\" title=\"University of Western Australia\">University of Western Australia</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Background\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Background</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Further_reading\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Further reading</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Background\">Background</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Rindos_affair&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Background\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In early 1989, <a href=\"/wiki/David_Rindos\" title=\"David Rindos\">David Rindos</a>, an <a href=\"/wiki/Archaeologist\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Archaeologist\">archaeologist</a> by qualification, was hired to fill a vacancy in the university's Department of Archaeology. Rindos commenced work on 13 June 1989. In 1990, the head of department, Dr <a href=\"/wiki/Sandra_Bowdler\" title=\"Sandra Bowdler\">Sandra Bowdler</a>, took study leave. Bowdler was the Foundation Professor of Archaeology. Rindos became acting head of department in her place.\n</p><p>Rindos later said that during his time as acting head, he was made aware of problems in the department, including <a href=\"/wiki/In-group_favoritism\" title=\"In-group favoritism\">favouritism</a> and affairs between students and staff members. In December 1990, Rindos wrote a <a href=\"/wiki/Memorandum\" title=\"Memorandum\">memo</a> to Professor Charles Oxnard, then-head of Agriculture and Science, detailing the allegations of <a href=\"/wiki/Academic_misconduct\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Academic misconduct\">academic misconduct</a> against Bowdler.\n</p><p>In June 1992, Rindos' three-year probation period was complete and a decision on <a href=\"/wiki/Tenure\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Tenure\">tenure</a> was due. In May, the Vice-Chancellor, <a href=\"/wiki/Fay_Gale\" title=\"Fay Gale\">Fay Gale</a>, had extended the review period by six months after having received a memo from Dr Michael Partis, the new head of department. A Tenure Review Committee was formed as a result. After an hour of deliberation, the committee unanimously decided to deny tenure.\n</p><p>In July 1992 the Department of Archaeology was dissolved.\n</p><p>On 10 June 1993, Rindos was dismissed, effective 13 June.\n</p><p>In early 1996, the university's Senate announced an inquiry<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> into the denial of tenure to Rindos. The terms of reference of the inquiry did not extend to investigating the allegations of misconduct against Bowdler.\n</p><p>The <a href=\"/wiki/Western_Australian_Legislative_Council\" title=\"Western Australian Legislative Council\">Western Australian Legislative Council</a> investigated the denial of tenure to Rindos. Their report<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> was delivered in December 1997.\n</p><p>David Rindos died in 1996.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Rindos_affair&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Rindos_v_Hardwick\" title=\"Rindos v Hardwick\">Rindos v Hardwick</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Rindos_affair&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"reflist\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Day, Michael (29 February 1996). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://wings.buffalo.edu/anthropology/Rindos/Press/96-02-29.west\">\"UWA inquiry must be credible, says Rindos\"</a>. <i>The West Australian</i>. Perth.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+West+Australian&amp;rft.atitle=UWA+inquiry+must+be+credible%2C+says+Rindos&amp;rft.date=1996-02-29&amp;rft.aulast=Day&amp;rft.aufirst=Michael&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwings.buffalo.edu%2Fanthropology%2FRindos%2FPress%2F96-02-29.west&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARindos+affair\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.parliament.wa.gov.au/Parliament/commit.nsf/%28Download+Lookup%29/81EEAE9D6898C36148257831003E942E?opendocument\">\"The events surrounding the denial of tenure to the late Dr David Rindos by the University of Western Australia\"</a>. <i>Public Administration Committee</i>. <a href=\"/wiki/Parliament_of_Western_Australia\" title=\"Parliament of Western Australia\">Parliament of Western Australia</a>. 4 December 1997<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">15 August</span> 2012</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Public+Administration+Committee&amp;rft.atitle=The+events+surrounding+the+denial+of+tenure+to+the+late+Dr+David+Rindos+by+the+University+of+Western+Australia&amp;rft.date=1997-12-04&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.parliament.wa.gov.au%2FParliament%2Fcommit.nsf%2F%2528Download%2BLookup%2529%2F81EEAE9D6898C36148257831003E942E%3Fopendocument&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARindos+affair\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Rindos_affair&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.timeshighereducation.co.uk/story.asp?storyCode=93477&amp;sectioncode=26\">Times Higher Education Supplement: Sacked lecturer wins inquiry</a